description:
For those interested, this will be the first meetup (over coffee and drinks) with the opportunity to have a dialogue regarding the current situations in the Middle East. Not everything will be covered, but it's a start. Anyone is welcome(expertise not necessary). The intention is to engage as a group (respecting each other) and try to understand the issues and their origins.

Join us!


Please RSVP before September 14th (Cafe has limited seating) if you plan to attend .

See you on the 16th of September!

Joyce
name: Identity Crisis in Middle East Nations?

description:
Come join us for yet another new discussion that encompasses the world at large regarding the current ISIS bombing. Bring friends/colleagues if you'd like!

Kind regards! 

Joyce
name: Legitimacy and possible implications of ISIS bombing
